JOTJPN - Open Source php script to manage and resell cloud hosting. Currently it support digitalocean droplets to resell.

Installation instructions:

1) Upload zip and etract files.
2) Create mysql database and import database.sql file (available in zip file)
3) Open confi.php and database.php and update variables (located at application/config/)

Thats it!

Admin url: yourdomain_installation_path/index.php/login/admin
Username:  admin
Password:  admin

Client loin url: yourdomain_installation_path/index.php/login/


For technical support and modification contact us on https://jotjpn.com 


